---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Automation for Dairy and Cheese Manufacturers — Formic"
  description="Too much overtime, not enough people. Downtime that stinks worse than spoiled milk. Cheese and dairy production is demanding — Formic makes it easier. Fully managed palletizing and case packing under one monthly fee."
  ogTitle="Automation for Dairy and Cheese Manufacturers — Formic"
  ogDescription="Fully managed robotic palletizing and case packing for dairy and cheese manufacturers. No CapEx, deployed in weeks."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/results/dairy-and-cheese" slot="head" />
  <style is:global slot="head">
    .ind-yt-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;aspect-ratio:16/9;background:#000;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
    .ind-yt-wrap iframe{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:0}
    .ind-qbox{background:var(--white);padding:34px 32px;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);margin:18px 0 22px}
    .ind-qbox blockquote{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:19px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.5;color:var(--black);margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-.005em}
    .ind-qbox .ind-qattr{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey)}
    .ind-faq{border-top:1px solid var(--lgrey);padding:22px 0}
    .ind-faq:last-child{border-bottom:1px solid var(--lgrey)}
    .ind-faq dt{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:18px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black);margin:0 0 8px}
    .ind-faq dd{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.65;color:var(--mgrey);margin:0}
  </style>

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/results">Results</a><span class="sep">/</span>Dairy &amp; Cheese
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Industry · Dairy &amp; Cheese</div>
    <h1>Automation for <br><em>dairy and cheese manufacturers</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Too much overtime, not enough people. Downtime that stinks worse than spoiled milk. Sound familiar? Cheese production is demanding. We make it easier.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/stories/rumiano-cheese/1745598936-rumiano-1.jpg">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Automate NOW · dairy &amp; cheese</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">$0 CapEx · Deployed in weeks</div>
      <h2>Automate your line. <em>Deploy in weeks</em>.</h2>
      <p>Palletizing and case packing that work from day one. No hiring. No retraining. No headaches. Just consistent output that's smooth as butter.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Configured for cold storage and refrigerated production environments</li>
        <li>Handles 40-lb bulk blocks, shredded pouches, tubs, and yogurt buckets</li>
        <li>Removes operators from the highest-strain stacking and case-pack tasks</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact/get-a-quote" class="larr">Talk to a dairy automation engineer →</a>
      <a class="dl-btn" href="/downloads/Formic-Best-Practices-Dairy-Cheese-Masters-Gallery.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="dl-btn-icon" aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
        <span class="dl-btn-text">
          <span class="dl-btn-title">Dairy &amp; cheese best practices guide</span>
          <span class="dl-btn-meta">PDF · 1.7 MB</span>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/rumiano-cheese/1745598936-rumiano-1.jpg" alt="Formic palletizing cell at Rumiano Cheese — organic cheese production" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Cheese palletizing · 24/7</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/masters-gallery/1765387022-r52_6416-1.jpg" alt="Patrick Henson at Masters Gallery / Rumiano Cheese plant" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Rumiano · Masters Gallery</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">Customer story</div>
      <h2>Rumiano Cheese eliminates manual palletizing <em>to improve throughput</em>.</h2>
      <div class="ind-qbox">
        <blockquote>"It was the level of support Formic provides. We don't have to have someone trained in advanced robotics on site, and knowing that Formic can come to our aid when we need it fairly quickly was what drove our decision."</blockquote>
        <div class="ind-qattr">Patrick Henson · General Manager, Masters Gallery / Rumiano Cheese</div>
      </div>
      <a href="/stories/rumiano-cheese" class="larr">Read the Rumiano story →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dgrey">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">Customer story</div>
      <h2>Sunrise Family Farms <em>preserves tradition</em>.</h2>
      <div class="ind-qbox" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border-left-color:var(--orange)">
        <blockquote style="color:var(--white)">"Formic was a perfect match for us. You can own an automation system, but you never know what tomorrow brings. There's no high risk for us with Formic. If you have a shortfall, and a customer leaves, the equipment doesn't just sit there idle. We didn't need to spend money up front. A lot of troubleshooting is done remotely. The service is there. The reliability is there."</blockquote>
        <div class="ind-qattr" style="color:rgba(240,245,241,.65)">Sunrise Family Farms</div>
      </div>
      <a href="/stories/sunrise-family-farms" class="larr">Read the Sunrise Family Farms story →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/sunrise-family-farms/1756826112-screenshot-2025-09-02-at-8-15-01-am-2.png" alt="Sunrise Family Farms yogurt-bucket line" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Yogurt buckets · automated stacking</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 24px">
    <div class="db-tag">FAQ</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(30px,3.6vw,48px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.06;color:var(--black);margin:8px 0 22px">Dairy &amp; cheese automation <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">questions</em>.</h2>
    <dl style="margin:0">
      <div class="ind-faq"><dt>How do your systems hold up in cold storage and refrigerated dairy production?</dt><dd>Formic systems are built for cold, humid, condensation-prone environments. Every cell is configured for the specific room — cooler, brine tank, packaging room — with environmental validation during scoping.</dd></div>
      <div class="ind-faq"><dt>Will the robot handle the packaging formats we use for cheese blocks, shreds, or tubs?</dt><dd>40-lb bulk blocks, multi-pack shredded pouches, round tubs — grippers and end-of-arm tooling are spec'd per SKU. Gentle handling, proper orientation, reliable stacking.</dd></div>
      <div class="ind-faq"><dt>How does automation help our staffing and ergonomic challenges in cheese and dairy operations?</dt><dd>High-turnover, physically taxing roles — stacking, case packing — get automated across all three shifts. No CapEx, no robot techs to hire, and the work that's hardest on people goes to the robot.</dd></div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">Say "cheese" to better productivity</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--white);margin:8px 0 28px">Automate your dairy and cheese lines — <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">for $0 in CapEx</em>.</h2>
    <div class="ind-yt-wrap">
      <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SD0UMnNYR1E" title="Formic Full Service Automation" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Get started with automation<br><em>today</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="/contact/get-a-quote" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/results" class="btn-ctawh">All Industries</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
